<br>
I can only think of one who repeatedly let people die because they were too busy melee'ing to meditate and get mana back, or too busy watching themselves proc to heal.  They also were usually OOM from consistent DD's and chain stuns.<br>
<br>
I know another cleric who likes to melee a lot.  I very seldom see him sitting on his horse, which he looks ridiculous on as a dwarf.  But he has never missed a heal cause he was melee'ing.  He may make my heart skip a beat cause we're in tells making fun of bad group members or what not and his heal is late.  But he's still the best cleric I've grouped with enough to be able to make that judgement. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqfaces.com/photos2/blinkun_copy1.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
