<br>
at lower levels most clerics will try to max out their one hand bash and bash skills for their wonderful hammer of the future.<br>
<br>
You should prolly take it as a compliment that the cleric or healer was comfortable enough with your tanking that they could work on their other skills.<br>
<br>
